The following sample shows how you can delete a user:

```sh
curl -v -X DELETE \
  -H "Authorization:Bearer {ACCESS_TOKEN}" \
  -H "x-kii-appid:{APP_ID}" \
  -H "x-kii-appkey:{APP_KEY}" \
  "https://api.kii.com/api/apps/{APP_ID}/users/me"
```
